Pattern of pedal glands (
Figure 6
). UpG elliptical and smaller than MeG in anterior chaetigers, becoming larger than MeG in middle chaetigers. LoG absent in both anterior and middle chaetigers. MeG oblong and twice larger than PoG in middle chaetigers, becoming rounded and half as large as PoG in middle chaetigers. PoG becoming larger towards middle chaetigers.
